  [Excerpt] Yesterday the agonizing uncertainty over the 
layoffs announced at Christmas ended for Fokker production 
workers at Schiphol, Papendrecht, Ypenburg, and Woensdrecht. 
Today office and support staff will hear who will stay on. 
  A total of 1,100 people will be laid off, with 350 forming 
