<H3> <TI>   Two Injured in Grenade Explosion in Istanbul </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Two Injured in Grenade Explosion in Istanbul </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA2605181894 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 
GMT 26 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA2605181894 </F>
<F P=104>  Ankara TRT Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Turkish </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Announcer-read report over video] </F>
  [Text] Terrorists threw concussion grenades at the fast 
tramway station in Aksaray, Istanbul. Two persons were injured 
in the incident. Two terrorists placed a concussion grenade at 
the main entrance gate of the fast tramway station around 1745. 
Two as yet unidentified persons were slightly injured in the 
explosion. The explosion also caused slight damage at the 
station. 
  A bomb placed in a garbage can in front of a fast-food 
counter in Aksaray also exploded around the same time. No one 
was killed or injured in the explosion. Security forces are 
continuing their search operations to apprehend the terrorists. 

</TEXT>

