<H3> <TI>   Rescue Service Moves Headquarters To Croatia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Rescue Service Moves Headquarters To Croatia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2605191494 Stockholm Radio Sweden in English 1615 GMT 26 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD2605191494 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Meanwhile the Serbs have now definitely made it 
impossible for the Swedish rescue service to send their trucks 
with food and other supplies into eastern Bosnia from Belgrade. 
The Swedes are moving their headquarters now to Croatia and the 
white UN humanitarian convoys will be able to come to Bosnia 
from there. 

</TEXT>

