<F P=101> Inter-European Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   EC To Improve Baltic Information Infrastructure </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    EC To Improve Baltic Information Infrastructure </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2005134994 Brussels RAPID Database in English 20 May 
94--FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

