<F P=102>   PM2405141094 London THE TIMES in English 24 May 94 p 12 -- 
FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM2405141094 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
