<H3> <TI>   Health Department Warns of `Deadly Bacteria' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Health Department Warns of `Deadly Bacteria' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   PM2505161094 London THE TIMES in English 25 May 94 p 3--FOR 
OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> PM2505161094 </F>
<F P=104>  London THE TIMES </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


