<H3> <TI>   New Democratic Party of Left Leaders </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    New Democratic Party of Left Leaders </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR2005133894 Milan CORRIERE DELLA SERA in Italian 20 May 94 
p 3 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

