<H3> <TI>   Craxi To Surrender Passport After Recovery </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Craxi To Surrender Passport After Recovery </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BR1905092994 Rome ANSAMAIL Database in English 2129 GMT 18 
May 94 -- FOR OFFICIAL USE ONLY </F>

<F P=103> BR1905092994 </F>
<F P=104>  Rome ANSAMAIL Database </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
